eyboard instrument|keyboards]]\n*[[Reggie Lucas]]&nbsp;\u2013 producer of \"Ain't No Big Deal\"\n*David Williams&nbsp;\u2013 [[rhythm guitar]]\n*Bruce Gaitsch&nbsp;\u2013 [[electric guitar]]\n*John Putnam&nbsp;\u2013 [[Steel-string acoustic guitar|acoustic guitar]], electric guitar\n*[[Fred Zarr]]&nbsp;\u2013 additional keyboards\n*Johnathan Moffett&nbsp;\u2013 [[Percussion instrument|percussion]]\n*Billy Meyers&nbsp;\u2013 [[string section|string arrangement]]\n*[[Siedah Garrett]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Backing vocalist|background vocals]]\n*Edie Lehmann&nbsp;\u2013 background vocals\n\nCredits adapted from the album's liner notes.<ref>{{cite AV media notes|others=Madonna|title=True Blue|year=1986|type=Liner notes|publisher=Warner Bros. Records|id=925442-2}}</ref>\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n!Chart (1986)\n!Peak<br />position\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Australia ([[Kent Music Report]])<ref name=\"kent\">{{cite news|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1986-08-22/entertainment/8603030190_1_preach-higher-love-papa|title=Madonna Preaches Her Message to Appreciative Worldwide Audience|date=August 22, 1986|last=DeKnock|first= Jan|work=[[Chicago Tribune]]|accessdate=March 7, 2009}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n{{singlechart|Austria|4|artist=Madonna|song=Papa Don't Preach|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"aut\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Flanders|1|artist=Madonna|song=Papa Don't Preach|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"belfla\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Canadatopsingles|1|chartid=0710|artist=Madonna|song=Papa Don't Preach|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"canrpm\"}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[European Hot 100 Singles]] (''[[Music & Media]]'')<ref name=\"euro\">{{cite web|url=https://www.americanradiohistory.com/UK/Music-and-Media/80s/1986/M&M-1986-09-20.pdf|title=European Hot 100 Singles|page=12|work=[[Music & Media]]|date=September 20, 1986|accessdate=April 4, 2020}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|European Airplay Top 50 (''[[Music & Media]]'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.americanradiohistory.com/UK/Music-and-Media/80s/1986/M&M-1986-09-13.pdf|title=European Airplay Top 50|page=4|work=[[Music & Media]]|date=September 13, 1986|accessdate=April 4, 2020}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n{{singlechart|France|3|artist=Madonna|song=Papa Don't Preach|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"fra\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Germany2|2|songid=1465|artist=Madonna|song=Papa Don't Preach|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Iceland ([[R\u00daV]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ruv.is/persona/madonna|publisher=[[R\u00daV]]|title= Madonna Chart History| accessdate=May 24, 2017}}</ref>\n| 2\n|-\n{{singlechart|Ireland2|1|artist=Madonna|song=Papa Don't Preach|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"irl\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Dutch40|2|artist=Madonna|song=Papa Don't Preach|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"dt40\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Dutch100|1|artist=Madonna|song=Papa Don't Preach|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"dt100\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|New Zealand|3|artist=Madonna|song=Papa Don't Preach|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"nzc\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Norway|1|artist=Madonna|song=Papa Don't Preach|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"nor\"}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Poland ([[Lista Przeboj\u00f3w Programu Trzeciego|LP3]])<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://lp3.polskieradio.pl/notowania/?numer=236|title=Top 30 Poland|magazine=[[Lista Przeboj\u00f3w Programu Trzeciego|LP3]]|date=April 29, 1989|accessdate=April 1, 2018|format=PDF}}</ref>\n| 2\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Spain ([[Productores de M\u00fasica de Espa\u00f1a|AFYVE]])<ref name=\"spain\"/>\n|align=\"center\"|4\n|-\n{{singlechart|Sweden|6|artist=Madonna|song=Papa Don't Preach|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|ref