lechart|UKsinglesbyname|1|artist=Madonna|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"uk\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardhot100|1|artist=Madonna|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"bbhot100\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardadultcontemporary|16|artist=Madonna|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"ac\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboarddanceclubplay|4|artist=Madonna|rowheader=true|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"dance\"}}\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Year-end charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! Chart (1986)\n! Position\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Australia (Kent Music Report)<ref name=\"Kent\">{{Cite book|title=Australian Chart Book 1970\u20131992|last=Kent|first=David|title-link=Kent Music Report|authorlink=David Kent (historian)|publisher=Australian Chart Book, St Ives, N.S.W |year=1993|isbn=0-646-11917-6}}</ref>\n| 9\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| Austria (\u00d63 Austria Top 40)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://austriancharts.at/1986_single.asp|title=Jahreshitparaden 1986|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=April 4, 2011|language=German}}</ref>\n| 21\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| Belgium (Ultratop Flanders)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/annual.asp?year=1986|title=Annuale Rapports 1986|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=December 17, 2015}}</ref>\n| 6\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| Canada Top Singles (''RPM'')<ref name=\"rpmyearend\"/>\n| 13\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| Germany (Official German Charts)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/charts/single-jahr/for-date-1986 |title=Top 100 Single-Jahrescharts|language=German |publisher=Offiziellecharts.de |accessdate=5 December 2015}}</ref>\n| 18\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| Netherlands (Single Top 100)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dutchcharts.nl/jaaroverzichten.asp?year=1986&cat=s|title=Jaaroverzichten 1986|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=April 4, 2011|language=Dutch}}</ref>\n| 13\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| New Zealand (Recorded Music NZ)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=3875|title=NZ Top 40 Year end 1986|publisher=RMNZ|accessdate=December 17, 2015}}</ref>\n| 13\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| Switzerland (Schweizer Hitparade)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hitparade.ch/year.asp?key=1986|title=Jahreshitparaden 1986|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=April 4, 2011|language=German}}</ref>\n| 14\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|UK Singles (Official Charts Company)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mostynhouseschool.com/pg/80/top50/uk86.htm|title=End Of Year Chart&nbsp;\u2014 Top 50 Singles of 1986|accessdate=November 28, 2012}}</ref>\n| 8\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| US ''Billboard'' Hot 100<ref name=\"bbyearend\"/>\n| 29\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|US Dance Club Songs (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/charts/archivesearch/article_display/855390|title=Dance Sales Singles/Albums 1986 (Top Dance Singles)|date=December 31, 1986|accessdate=July 19, 2011|work=Billboard|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121008123239/http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/charts/archivesearch/article_display/855390|archivedate=October 8, 2012}}</ref>\n| 29\n|}\n\n===All-time charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n!Chart (1958\u20132018)\n!Position\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|US ''Billboard'' Hot 100<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100-60th-anniversary|title=Greatest of All Time Hot 100 Songs|work=Billboard|access-date=August 13, 2018}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|579\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Certifications==\n{{Certification Table Top}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Belgium|type=single|artist=Madonna|title=Papa Don't Preach|award=Gold|salesamount=100,000|certref=<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.americanradiohistory.com/Archive-Music-and-Media/80s/1986/M&M-1986-12-27.pdf|title=European Gold & Platinum Awards 1986|magazine=[[Music & Media]]|page=33|date=December 27, 1986|accessdate=July 7, 2019}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=France|artist=Madonna|title=Papa Don't Preach|type=single|award=Silver|recent=false|relyear=1986|certyear=1986|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"snep\"}}\n{{Certification Table Entry |region=Japan ([[Oricon|Oricon Charts]]) |nocert=yes |salesamount=34,410|salesref=<ref>{{cite book |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |title=Oricon Album Chart Book: Complete Edition 1970\u20132005. |url= |location=[[Roppongi|Roppongi, Tokyo]] |publisher=[[Oricon Charts]] |page= |date=2006 |isbn=4-87131-077-9}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United Kingdom|artist=Madonna|title=Papa Don't Preach|type=single|award=Gold|relyear=1986|certyear=1986|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"bpi\"|salesamount=651,000|salesref= <ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/madonna-s-official-top-40-biggest-selling-singles__8266/ |title=Madonna's Official Top 40 Biggest Selling Singles|last=Myers |first=Justin|date=August 16, 2017|work=Official Charts Company|accessdate=September 10, 2017}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United States|artist=Madonna|title=Papa Don't Preach|type=single|award=Gold|relyear=1986|certyear=1986|accessdate=December 14, 2014|refname=\"riaa\"}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom}}\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of Billboard Hot 100 number-one singles of 1986]]\n*[[List of European number-one hits of 1986]]\n*[[List of number-one singles in Australia during the 1980s]]\n*[[List of number-one singles of 1986 (Canada)]]\n*[[List of number-one singles of 1986 (Ireland)]]\n*[[List of number-one hits of 1986 (Italy)]]\n*[[List of UK Singles Chart number ones of the 1980s]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==References==\n{{refbegin|30em}}\n*{{Cite book\n |last=Bielen\n |first=Kenneth G.\n |title=The Lyrics of Civility: Biblical Images and Popular Music Lyrics in American Culture\n |year=1999\n |publisher=[[Routledge]]\n |isbn=0-8153-3193-2\n |ref=harv\n }}\n*{{Cite book\n |last=Clerk\n |first=Carol\n |title=Madonnastyle\n |year=2002\n |publisher=[[Music Sales Group|Omnibus Press]]\n |isbn=0-